There is no difference between syle in between the tags and css.
css are used to control the styling of the web page.


<tagname style="property:value;property:value;........">
property --
          background-color
          color
          font-family
          font
          font-size
          text-align
          width
          height

background-color or color values are red, blue, green etc
font, font-family vales are times new roman, calibar, etc  
font-size it is represented with percantage(%) like 100%, 200% etc
width, height it is represented with Pixels(px) like 230px, 3000px etc
text-align values are center, middle, start, end, justify, start etc

There are other properties like max-width, max-height etc
